// Given n players with (score, name) pairs,
// print them sorted: highest score first.
// Ties broken alphabetically by name (ascending).
// n ≤ 10^5
// Example input:
// 4
// 95 Alice
// 87 Bob
// 95 Charlie
// 87 Alice

